			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			This quest is related to the Thex Mallet and the Ring of the Dead/Reaper of the Dead quest.<BR>
<BR>
If a Necro or SK hands the Testimonial over, they are given a phrase to speak to Kizdean Gix.  When you do this, Gix gives you a letter to give to his assistant Lrodd.  But Lrodd is dead...<BR>
<BR>
I have done this quest twice as there are two items to be gained from it.  I have only recieved the Reaper of the Dead - a 2h Sycthe with LoH abaility - 1 charge.  I don't know if it can be recharged.  The other item is the ring of the dead that allows SKs to bind anywhere, it may have been removed!<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Nenadar<BR>
