			Ok Here goes my 2cp. I did this quest lastnight and this is what I found. First the Light Elf in Lavastorm is a waste of time you don't need to kill him to get the Thex Mallet quest. Goto Gix in WC and say to him Utalk Adarev Otcin and he will give you the note to give to LLrod on the 1st floor of Befallen. As a note I have found that if you don't cap each of the first letters Gix does note give me the note in fact he ignors that I spoke to him. Give the note to LLrod and spawns the Mummie Windstream. Kill him and get the handle. Go back and kill the Elf SK and get the last 2 pieces to the mallet combine them and you get the Thex Mallet simple huh. Any way the mallet itself if your an SK or Necro is usless as a weapon but you can turn it in to get a reaper of the dead the Ring of the Dead is no longer available in this quest. Not sure if its available at all. Also I would not recomend doing this quest until about 16th Lvl and taking a full group with you Windstream is about 22lvl. <BR>
